In order to reproduce the problem, follow the steps below:
1. Go to a record page;
2. Click on the "Edit" button;
3. Click on "New version" in the deposit form;
4. Click on "Create new version".

- Fixes issue with licenses not being sorted alphabetically.
  (closes 302)

Signed-off-by: Lars Holm Nielsen lars.holm.nielsen@cern.ch

