E.g. submitting

```
"related_identifiers": [
        {"relation": "cites", "identifier":"bla bla bla"}
    ],
```

will reply:

```
{
    "errors": [
        {
            "code": 10, 
            "field": "related_identifiers-0-identifier", 
            "message": "Not a valid persistent identifier"
        }, 
        {
            "code": 10, 
            "field": "related_identifiers-0", 
            "message": "identifier"
        }, 
        {
            "code": 10, 
            "field": "related_identifiers", 
            "message": {
                "identifier": [
                    "Not a valid persistent identifier"
                ]
            }
        }
    ], 
    "message": "Bad request", 
    "status": 400
}
```

expected something like:

```
{
    "errors": [
        {
            "code": 10, 
            "field": "related_identifiers", 
            "message": {
                "identifier": [
                    "Not a valid persistent identifier"
                ]
            }
        }
    ], 
    "message": "Bad request", 
    "status": 400
}
```

E.g. https://zenodo.org/communities/?p=biosyslit should return the same as https://zenodo.org/communities/?p=Biodiversity+literature+repository

